data.description: Seller to offer $5000 closing cost with full price offer. Look no further! Completely updated ranch home on a very quiet lot in the country.  This home was beautifully updated in 2022. The home was entirely painted inside as well as new flooring, light fixtures, doors, granite counter tops, new cabinets, appliances, both bathrooms totally redone, new hvac, hw heater, well pump all done in 2022. No HOA or Restrictive Covenants. Make this your new home today! Great starter home for under 300k. Come on out and take a look.
